  21,103,"Suninoytaa…ìe …óen∆¥ere mawnde nden, Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen no ja…ì…ìoo…ìe […ìe wi'a:] \"Ko ndee woni √ëalaande mo'on, nden nde laatino…óon hi…óon fodee"
